      <div>

<p>This independent body was put together to develop a long-term strategy for roads and a commitment to major investment in street management and urban design.</p>

<p>The RTF report, published in July 2013, set out a view of how London could cope with major population growth and stay a vibrant, accessible and attractive world city.</p>

<p>An interactive map, case studies, technical notes and more are available on the <a href="/corporate/publications-and-reports/rtf-supporting-documents">RTF supporting documents page</a>.</p>

<p>The Mayor of London's vision for London's streets is set out in the <a href="/corporate/about-tfl/the-mayors-transport-strategy">Mayor's Transport Strategy</a>.</p>
