<h2>Our response to the report</h2>


<p>We are responsible for roads that carry about a third of the Capital's traffic.</p>

<p>We responded to the RTF report in 2013 to explain our plans to improve London's roads and streets in partnership with the boroughs, developers and others.</p>

<p>Our response set out how we would deliver improvements in the short term, and do further, detailed studies to assess and develop longer-term RTF proposals.</p>

<p>The plans we set out in our RTF response were superseded by the <a href="/corporate/about-tfl/the-mayors-transport-strategy">2018 Mayor's Transport Strategy</a>.</p>
